Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoku Gosenzo San'e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ba–
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth! How are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God! Hey, Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1: Spring Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been gone for so many months,\Nbut nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must feel very relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the schools in the big\Ncity, the air nere is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in a place like this, it's difficult\Nto imagine anything ever changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your eyes are as distant as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell! You came back {\i1}today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've at least told me you were coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming here was a last minute decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay now? You know, your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It took longer than I thought, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to spend some time catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer's coming to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's researching my illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't know she was in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came here with me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm coming home with you. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met at the front gate a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why she was absent last period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only missed school for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a new transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred to this school a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hiraga Gen. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an original pen from Howard University?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only sold on the Howard campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it when I was on vacation earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had one of those too, but I lost it in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had my initials engraved in it. I really liked it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer is coming to pick you up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should get some medicine from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, you need to call me Sakurako-sensei here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Sakurako-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mitsuko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My symptoms are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was in my genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something inherited...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still. I'm going to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially my daughter, Ayumi.\NShe talked about you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen? Gen! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were in here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer's here to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Okay. Well, Mitsuko-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, living a celebrity's life in America?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I had a hot and lovely night life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Gen was recovering from his\Nillness, he was with me every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I was asking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please excuse my clumsiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what were the results of Gen's analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After analyzing him at the research\Ncenter at Howard University,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered that there was a mismatched\Ngene in his 22nd chromosome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How that mutated gene will affect Gen's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're still researching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you researching it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twice a day, we shoot radiation\Ndirectly into his bone marrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This inhibits further growth of the\Nstrange matter in his blood cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've tried this treatment for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we've run current through the sympathetic\Nnerves to weaken them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But Gen has been trying his\Nhardest to control it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you the whole time you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we return to the way we were before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a blood disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the extent of your feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a little while would suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you care for me in even the slightest way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than when Jennifer does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Sorry! I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you'd probably rather not talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something going on between those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a normal fainting spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're under a misapprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong has happened\Nbetween Hiraga-kun and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know how you feel about him.\NWhy would I betray you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga-kun hasn't been back in Japan for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's going to be a bit distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So being moody about it won't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until he settles back into his old life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you have class, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch over this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you know, if you beat around the bush too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}someone else might steal him from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fainted during recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fell, you must have hit something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. May I return to the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to rest a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my class...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like the type of person who skips class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone's there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoh-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come right away. A student has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel nauseous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really a bite mark from a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you think Beth did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would have no reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No "reason" to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see this, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using this device to fulfill her energy needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth is able to live as normal a life as the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's what you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you had this device?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This device has been in the family for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably as far back as the Heian era.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Heian era?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's almost like Western magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Western magic and Eastern sorcery\Nare more similar than one might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When their motives are the same, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I researched both and discovered the best mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:21:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hiraga family has since fallen victim to a cruel fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your eternally youthful body and\NGen's illness are from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have asked you to help research\Nthis problem with modern methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Gen's illness really under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, it's totally suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Modern medicine will cure him completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! You big stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you. Happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just know that I'm rooting for you, with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that! Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher told me to assemble the research materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's not your fault if they're not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that teacher's scary when he's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice that you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you seem kind of distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Americans reconnect,\Ndon't they hug each other really tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you hug Jennifer all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but she always initiates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should try initiating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you were in America...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You forgot about me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I didn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought about you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never forgot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.91,0:25:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<•>{-)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Etsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.09,0:25:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she on the athletic field?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.26,0:25:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.39,0:25:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe she's in the shower or the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.97,0:25:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.02,0:25:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.88,0:27:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Zoku Gosenzou San'e:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.67,0:27:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furnace.
